{"tid":2302327,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"粵閩公安發「數碼ID」稱保私隱","createTime":"2020-11-27T04:41:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-27T05:10:18.000Z","uid":42804,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e8d6beb13b69896d4da100395ad20d282639919e","tid":2302327,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T04:41:19.000Z","msg":"網絡身份證｜粵閩公安發「數碼ID」稱保私隱 分析：快捷監控 可即停某人上網<br />\n <a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201127/KIHG6SVROJCUXMKZMFFF5S6SPA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201127%2FKIHG6SVROJCUXMKZMFFF5S6SPA%2F&d=jO1S1Ej7eDj8oQYGBWUFpAz7jHi%2Fw8vyA5J9XtqU0Cw%3D&h=6db2412f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201127%2FKIHG6SVROJCUXMKZMFFF5S6SPA%2F&h=7f90970f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201127/KIHG6SVROJCUXMKZMFFF5S6SPA/</a><br />\n<br />\n據指，這種稱作「居民身份網絡可信憑證」（網證）的，是CTID平台（國家「互聯網+」可信身份認證平台）簽發的權威網絡身份憑證，以二維碼等去標識化技術，取代輸入身份資料，實現不洩露身份訊息的前提下，完成身份認證。<br />\n<br />\n要取得網證，申請人要向警方提供人臉、指紋及身份證晶片等生物與個人資料。官方宣稱，網證採用國家級加密算法生成，綁定申請者的生物特徵及身份證，並有多重密碼，極難被偽冒，即使遺失手機也要人臉辨識，認為它可杜絕身份被盜用的危險。日後使用任何要實名登記的服務，只要使用網證便可，毋須再動用實體證件。"},{"pid":"492492a18ea7e035dad62ffa2045a4134a9277a7","tid":2302327,"uid":278524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T04:53:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eb23313c97e2b6356609ea5dcb25d406c1c89ff","tid":2302327,"uid":380132,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T04:54:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4485700e4541f896fa4be1e0e30767bf4e5b943b","tid":2302327,"uid":9542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T04:55:51.000Z","msg":"同懲教狗係廁所裝cam 話保障私隱一樣"},{"pid":"7adc6a08a2300598345c8aa82e1d059c3958ad8c","tid":2302327,"uid":8308,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T04:56:04.000Z","msg":"所以明點解美國要拆牆<br />\n因為中共只係剩下圍牆"},{"pid":"d6fc9a885e0e188f06a478353c412b5aa5e103ea","tid":2302327,"uid":42804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T05:10:18.000Z","msg":"健康碼都唔夠呢個直接<br />\n健康碼可以用二手機開<br />\n但係而家中國乜嘢都實名制下，連申通電話號碼都要實名登記，再加上網上身分證，基本上再無地方走盞。"}]}